For proper configuration of Netapp cluster mode san the following property is required {{one.storage.vservername}} However, it is not found thus storage controller can never become enabled.

{code}
[root@a-35 ~]# euctl one.storage.vservername=euca-vserver
euctl: error (ModifyPropertyValueType): Failed to set property: No such property: one.storage.vservername
{code}
